"```sql\nSELECT \n    (SUM(CASE WHEN c.Currency = 'CZK' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN c.Currency = 'EUR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) AS Amount_of_more_SMEs\nFROM \n    customers c\nWHERE \n    c.Segment = 'SME';\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the difference between the number of SMEs paying in Czech koruna (CZK) and those paying in euros (EUR) by counting the occurrences of each currency for SMEs in the `customers` table."